{"tid":346427,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"場場入十幾球都輸咗 細路失望家長震怒","createTime":"2017-08-04T02:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T04:13:01.000Z","uid":4661,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66ab0bf409f2f83d178348d36ca2791acf8f52fd","tid":346427,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170804/large/1501810170_6b7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170804%2Flarge%2F1501810170_6b7d.jpg&h=f4706694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n踢足球要贏當然靠入波，可是，一場由湖南省體育總會主辦的小童足球賽，這隊場場贏對手超過10球的球隊，卻竟然要將冠軍王座拱手給予一隊連決賽都進不了的隊伍！這無理結果讓很多家長憤怒，激動地與主辦單位理論，未料獲得的回覆竟是：點讚最多的球隊才是冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n這場「第二屆世幼盃幼兒玩足球活動（湖南區）」由湖南省體育總會主辦，湖南虎童足球俱樂部與《長沙晚報》承辦，上月底進行比賽。可是，決賽後卻有家長大表不滿。其中一名家長稱，兒子的球隊每場比賽都大勝，「每一場比賽都是10幾比0贏下來的，但最後我們居然不是冠軍，點讚最多的球隊獲得了第一名」。<br />\n<br />\n不少在決賽勝出球隊的小童都感到十分失望，其中一名家長稱：「孩子等這個獎盃都已經等了1年，去年拿了冠軍，獎盃都不發，今年我們又來了，卻告訴我們，要點讚率第一才能拿冠軍！」有家長更怒斥：「點讚是甚麼，就是網絡刷票，是每個人都可以去刷票，都可以去操作！」<br />\n<br />\n面對不滿的家長，主辦單位的工作人員辯稱，靠點讚定冠軍，是要「淡化幼兒足球的競​​技性」，「不想說某個孩子進了球他就是第一名」。<br />\n<br />\n工作人員的說法引發網民公憤：「其實都是主辦方搞的鬼，1塊錢10票，看誰錢多人脈多！」「如果世界盃也是點讚的話，估計中國每屆都拿冠軍，人口多，準贏！」"},{"pid":"843e9702d97bd0aebfb274e8d29d1d432dce26dd","tid":346427,"uid":19552,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來阿仙奴盃都未最勁"},{"pid":"2740f6bba77b71c3c233910b978e3cda3d3fe7ff","tid":346427,"uid":28,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:59:09.000Z","msg":"仲勁過酋長盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3b050ff494c02543c8e6e4d4a1581dd5e4bc16","tid":346427,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5351255ba5dd14b81e45698af28381bdea7ceeee","tid":346427,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:59:27.000Z","msg":"阿"},{"pid":"0d71baf688d3972eae40ea6a23c5793cfe5666d1","tid":346427,"uid":54344,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:59:35.000Z","msg":"「淡化幼兒足球的競​​技性」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e08902218c36f1b8adfa5060f3db63596a0fc4d","tid":346427,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:02:03.000Z","msg":"中國所有野就係咁荒謬<br />\n<br />\n連個家長都係, 明知上年都已經唔發獎盃今年又去, 痴撚線國家"},{"pid":"41da360682bf798b1fb5e26744072732995b1f7a","tid":346427,"uid":127269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:04:39.000Z","msg":"有冇原文link??"},{"pid":"fa57d7097e92303a1aac17e814bda3b9272e26ff","tid":346427,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c67cc68effecab5f98f73e010f359f68c126045","tid":346427,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇原文link??</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170804/57038947\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170804%2F57038947&d=GOD2VbLj2pT0IRhDxHdDR2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=f3608e39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170804%2F57038947&h=defc7ff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.